Title: The U(1) and Strong CP Problem From the Loop Formulation Perspective
Authors: H. Fort and R. Gambini (IFFC, Montevideo, Uruguay)
Comments: 4 pages, revtex
\\
  We show how the gauge invariant formulation of QCD in terms of loops is free
from a hidden $\theta$ parameter and offers an alternative way to solve the
$U(1)_A$ puzzle.
